flowchart TD
    Start["Does your type contain self-references?"]
    Start -->|No| Unpin["Implements Unpin automatically"]
    Start -->|Yes| NoUnpin["Add PhantomPinned to opt out"]

    Unpin --> Safe["Pin::new works safely"]
    Safe --> Escape["Can unpin and move freely"]

    NoUnpin --> Unsafe["Must use Pin::new_unchecked (unsafe)"]
    Unsafe --> Stuck["Cannot get &mut T through safe code"]
    Stuck --> Guarantee["Value stays in place"]
